The Old Republic is dismantled and the Galactic Republic is formed.
A partnership of planets and peoples determined to keep peace in the galaxy.
The people of the Galactic Republic live without war for a thousand years.

Darth Plagueis and Darth Sidious are the latest Sith and Sith Master.
Darth Sidious learns everything he can from Plagueis and then murders him in his sleep.
In his quest to create the perfect Sith apprentice and eventual army to overthrow the Jedi and rule the galaxy,
Sidious creates at least two beings by force manipulation.
He hides these beings in the galaxy and treies to influence 
and corrupt their hearts and minds from the moment of their conception.